<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="64" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1437,787,1101]" pageId="8" pageNumber="64">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,267,788,814]" pageId="8" pageNumber="64">Remarks.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authorityName="Friedrich" authorityYear="1950" box="[275,451,787,813]" class="Polychaeta" family="Pilargidae" genus="Glyphohesione" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="8" pageNumber="64" phylum="Annelida" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[275,451,787,813]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="64">Glyphohesione</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was described by 
<bibRefCitation author="Friedrich, H." box="[677,873,787,814]" pageId="8" pageNumber="64" pagination="171 - 177" refId="ref13197" refString="Friedrich, H. (1950) Zwei neue Bestandteile in der Fauna der Nordsee. Zoologischer Anzeiger, 145, 171 - 177." type="journal article" year="1950">Friedrich (1950)</bibRefCitation>
as a monospecific genus, with 
<typeStatus box="[1254,1305,788,814]" pageId="8" pageNumber="64">type</typeStatus>
species 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Friedrich" authorityYear="1950" class="Polychaeta" family="Pilargidae" genus="Glyphohesione" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="8" pageNumber="64" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="klatti">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="64">G. klatti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
classified as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Grube" authorityYear="1850" box="[372,509,823,849]" class="Polychaeta" family="Hesionidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="8" pageNumber="64" phylum="Annelida" rank="family">Hesionidae</taxonomicName>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Eliason, A." box="[521,695,823,850]" pageId="8" pageNumber="64" pagination="1 - 97" refId="ref13009" refString="Eliason, A. (1962) Undersokningar over Oresund, 41: Weitere Untersuchungen uber die Polychaetenfauna des Oresunds. Lunds Universitets Arsskrift, 58 (9), 1 - 97." type="journal article" year="1962">Eliason (1962)</bibRefCitation>
redescribed 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Friedrich" authorityYear="1950" box="[847,944,823,850]" class="Polychaeta" family="Pilargidae" genus="Glyphohesione" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="8" pageNumber="64" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="klatti">
<emphasis box="[847,867,824,850]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="64">G</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[883,944,823,849]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="64">klatti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, as belonging to the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="McIntosh" authorityYear="1878" box="[1268,1429,823,849]" class="Polychaeta" family="Pilargidae" genus="Ancistrosyllis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="8" pageNumber="64" phylum="Annelida" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1268,1429,823,849]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="64">Ancistrosyllis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, placing it in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Saint-Joseph" authorityYear="1899" box="[303,427,859,885]" class="Polychaeta" family="Pilargidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="8" pageNumber="64" phylum="Annelida" rank="family">Pilargidae</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Friedrich" authorityYear="1950" box="[438,614,859,885]" class="Polychaeta" family="Pilargidae" genus="Glyphohesione" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="8" pageNumber="64" phylum="Annelida" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[438,614,859,885]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="64">Glyphohesione</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has also been considered a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Chamberlin" authorityYear="1919" box="[1174,1278,859,885]" class="Polychaeta" family="Pilargidae" genus="Synelmis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="8" pageNumber="64" phylum="Annelida" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1174,1278,859,885]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="64">Synelmis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Pettibone, M. H." pageId="8" pageNumber="64" pagination="155 - 207" refId="ref14706" refString="Pettibone, M. H. (1966) Revision of the Pilargidae (Annelida: Polychaeta), including descriptions of a new species and descriptions of the pelagic Podarmus ploa Chamberlin (Polynoide). Proceedings of the United States National Museum, 118 (3525), 155 - 207. https: // doi. org / 10.5479 / si. 00963801.118 - 3525.155" type="journal article" year="1966">Pettibone (1966)</bibRefCitation>
but it was re-established as a valid genus by 
<bibRefCitation author="Fitzhugh, K. &amp; Wolf, P. S." box="[773,1065,895,922]" pageId="8" pageNumber="64" pagination="1 - 16" refId="ref13159" refString="Fitzhugh, K. &amp; Wolf, P. S. (1990) Gross morphology of the brain of pilargid polychaetes: taxonomic and systematic implications. American Museum Novitates, 2992, 1 - 16." type="journal article" year="1990">Fitzhugh &amp; Wolf (1990)</bibRefCitation>
. Later, a revision of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Friedrich" authorityYear="1950" class="Polychaeta" family="Pilargidae" genus="Glyphohesione" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="8" pageNumber="64" phylum="Annelida" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="64">Glyphohesione</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
placed the genus back in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Grube" authorityYear="1850" box="[528,661,931,957]" class="Polychaeta" family="Hesionidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="8" pageNumber="64" phylum="Annelida" rank="family">Hesionidae</taxonomicName>
and suggested both families form a monophyletic group (Licher 1994). Those different hypotheses, both based on morphology, might be explained because of the phylogenetic rooting strategy; while 
<bibRefCitation author="Fitzhugh, K. &amp; Wolf, P. S." box="[507,804,1003,1030]" pageId="8" pageNumber="64" pagination="1 - 16" refId="ref13159" refString="Fitzhugh, K. &amp; Wolf, P. S. (1990) Gross morphology of the brain of pilargid polychaetes: taxonomic and systematic implications. American Museum Novitates, 2992, 1 - 16." type="journal article" year="1990">Fitzhugh &amp; Wolf (1990)</bibRefCitation>
used 
<taxonomicName authority=", Licher &amp; Westheide (1994)" authorityName="Licher &amp; Westheide" authorityYear="1994" box="[881,1331,1003,1030]" class="Polychaeta" family="Syllidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="8" pageNumber="64" phylum="Annelida" rank="family">
Syllidae, 
<bibRefCitation author="Licher, F. &amp; Westheide, W." box="[997,1331,1003,1030]" pageId="8" pageNumber="64" pagination="223 - 235" refId="ref13986" refString="Licher, F. &amp; Westheide, W. (1994) The phylogenetic position of the Pilargidae with a cladistic analysis of the taxon-facts and ideas. Memoires du Museum national d'Histoire naturelle, 162, 223 - 235." type="journal article" year="1994">Licher &amp; Westheide (1994)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
selected 
<taxonomicName authority="(Pleijel 2001)" baseAuthorityName="Pleijel" baseAuthorityYear="2001" box="[151,458,1039,1066]" class="Polychaeta" family="Hesionidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="8" pageNumber="64" phylum="Annelida" rank="family">
Hesionidae (
<bibRefCitation author="Pleijel, F." box="[299,449,1039,1066]" pageId="8" pageNumber="64" pagination="99 - 101" refId="ref14774" refString="Pleijel, F. (2001) Pilargidae. In: Rouse, G. W. &amp; Pleijel, F. (Eds.), Polychaetes. Oxford University Press, Oxford, pp. 99 - 101." type="book chapter" year="2001">Pleijel 2001</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
. Most recent taxonomic studies include 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Friedrich" authorityYear="1950" box="[931,1107,1039,1065]" class="Polychaeta" family="Pilargidae" genus="Glyphohesione" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="8" pageNumber="64" phylum="Annelida" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[931,1107,1039,1065]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="64">Glyphohesione</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Saint-Joseph" authorityYear="1899" box="[1145,1269,1039,1065]" class="Polychaeta" family="Pilargidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="8" pageNumber="64" phylum="Annelida" rank="family">Pilargidae</taxonomicName>
. There was no previous record of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Friedrich" authorityYear="1950" box="[377,553,1075,1101]" class="Polychaeta" family="Pilargidae" genus="Glyphohesione" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="8" pageNumber="64" phylum="Annelida" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[377,553,1075,1101]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="64">Glyphohesione</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species for 
<collectingCountry box="[697,773,1075,1101]" name="Brazil" pageId="8" pageNumber="64">Brazil</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
